- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of neural network architectures for NER. 
- cs.LG (Learning) is another possible category as the paper explores the use of embeddings for NER. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a relevant category as the paper focuses on neural network architectures for NER.
